<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.4">
<l>vāṉārmati potiyuñcaṭai maḻuvāḷiyo ṭorupāl</l>
<l>tāṉākiya talaivaṉṉava ṉamararkkati patiyām</l>
<l>tēṉārpoḻil taḻuvuṅciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tāṉāyaṉa taṭiyallatoṉ ṟaṟiyēṉaṭa yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The god who became himself on one side,</l>
<l rend="indent">along with the axe-bearer with matted locks</l>
<l>Where is bundled the moon which fills the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">is the overlord of the immortals;</l>
<l>I, his humble servant, do not know anything but the feet of the cattle herder</l>
<l>On a watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr embraced by nectar-filled groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
